{"tid":626863,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"班毒撚出街就連抬起頭既資格都冇","createTime":"2018-04-12T12:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T09:51:58.000Z","uid":156666,"like":8,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"acb31a2eb0abb2ba9e4bdc03ec68fc753f6a7c3d","tid":626863,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"今日同Fd係學校溫Mid-term <br />\n佢走左先 我就自己一個繼續温<br />\n咁突然有人行過我就下意識抬頭望左過去<br />\n<br />\n條女又望左過黎 但就之後突然西我臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n跟手行埋佢個Fd到話我望佢  <br />\n之後兩個就開始細細聲咁屌我 <br />\n( 行既過程一直西我 我似驚死我唔知講緊我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  諗住靜靜地溫個Mid-term都要比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班女人出街無啦啦幾個MK係到評頭品足都唔會開心啦<br />\n欺善怕惡 見我得一個人就即刻佮鳩我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦比佢搞到冇哂心機温書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n比佢屌完過左陣我就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係𥄫女, 條女成個肥絲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正評：下意識你老母咩 要温書就唔該番屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 負評：條女有病唔洗理"},{"pid":"3141be80688c6c4b406d157ac9c3e046927d60f2","tid":626863,"uid":132968,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:59:12.000Z","msg":"Your name"},{"pid":"99cb2cdc70c2a40140bbffa75a5ae57b2a9a6916","tid":626863,"uid":135445,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:59:22.000Z","msg":"比我就即場屌鳩佢<br />\n唔想比人望咪撚出街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇下邊個柒D"},{"pid":"bea891c2f42aecddbe626f89f4397ae1da63c410","tid":626863,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3141be806